Former public protector Thuli Madonsela and Advocate Dali Mpofu locked horns at Busisiwe Mkhwebane's impeachment inquiry. #dstv403 CAPE TOWN - Former Public Protector Thuli Madonsela and Advocate Dali Mpofu locked horns at Busisiwe Mkhwebane's impeachment inquiry. An annoyed Mpofu has been re-examining Madonsela and asked about her version submitted to the committee and the changes made in her affidavit. READ: Mkhwebane impeachment | Madonsela concerned over questions asked The committee is trying to determine whether Mkhwebane is fit to hold office. On Monday, raised concerns about questions Mkhwebane's legal team wanted her to answer.